ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2010-1
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT by adding the name of the Frog Lake First Nation along with the name of its governing body and the description of its reserves, where the Frog Lake GST-type tax law may apply.
